name: Jet Set Willy III
overview: It's hard to tell if this is the first true Jet Set Willy hack, but the programmers certainly decided to make this bold claim themselves when they christened this game Jet Set Willy III... as you would expect this is one of the less ambitious of the Willy hacks - not too surprising when you considered how soon it came out after the release of the second game on the system.
